1
00:00:03,563 --> 00:00:04,933
(Episode 59)

2
00:00:09,725 --> 00:00:10,765
Are these the test results?

3
00:00:11,565 --> 00:00:14,135
Yes, hurry up and open it.

4
00:00:15,435 --> 00:00:18,305
I was so nervous, I couldn't bring myself to open it.

5
00:00:24,205 --> 00:00:25,405
(DNA Parentage Test Report)

6
00:00:25,475 --> 00:00:27,175
(Subject 1: Park Hyun Jun, Subject 2: Song Geun Tae)

7
00:00:29,315 --> 00:00:31,415
(The results are indicative of a paternal relationship.)

8
00:00:35,415 --> 00:00:39,255
A 99 percent probability of paternity.

9
00:00:43,595 --> 00:00:44,665
Park Hyun Jun...

10
00:00:45,965 --> 00:00:47,895
really is Mr. Song's son.

11
00:00:49,935 --> 00:00:50,935
How could she...

12
00:00:53,005 --> 00:00:54,835
get pregnant with Mr. Song's child...

13
00:00:55,775 --> 00:00:56,945
and then do that to Myung Hui?

14
00:00:58,105 --> 00:00:59,545
It's because he was another man's child.

15
00:01:01,015 --> 00:01:03,545
She had to eliminate Min Jun, Chairman Park's only heir.

16
00:01:03,715 --> 00:01:06,415
For over 30 years, she's kept this huge secret.

17
00:01:07,485 --> 00:01:08,655
How did she keep it hidden?

18
00:01:10,525 --> 00:01:12,125
I'm going to Chairman Park right now...

19
00:01:13,125 --> 00:01:15,155
and tell him Park Hyun Jun is Mr. Song's son!

20
00:01:15,595 --> 00:01:16,595
I'll...

21
00:01:19,995 --> 00:01:21,165
What did you mean by that?

22
00:01:29,235 --> 00:01:31,175
What do you mean Hyun Jun is Mr. Song's son?

23
00:01:39,615 --> 00:01:41,285
I want to protect you from my father.

24
00:01:42,115 --> 00:01:43,125
Honestly,

25
00:01:45,255 --> 00:01:47,555
I don't really get this whole revenge thing.

26
00:01:50,125 --> 00:01:51,795
But seeing my father hurt you...

27
00:01:54,595 --> 00:01:55,765
is something I can't bear.

28
00:02:05,175 --> 00:02:06,175
Then...

29
00:02:08,045 --> 00:02:10,945
does this mean you'll accept my offer?

30
00:02:14,385 --> 00:02:15,785
I'll give you...

31
00:02:19,755 --> 00:02:20,795
everything I have.

32
00:02:35,005 --> 00:02:36,305
Are you going to tell Father?

33
00:02:36,605 --> 00:02:37,845
I'll handle it.

34
00:02:38,045 --> 00:02:40,015
That means Hyun Jun will get kicked out.

35
00:02:43,145 --> 00:02:45,515
What? You'll use my son?

36
00:02:46,755 --> 00:02:49,655
What if your son gets hurt again in the process?

37
00:02:52,255 --> 00:02:56,465
Hyun Jun didn't do anything wrong. This is too cruel to him.

38
00:02:57,495 --> 00:02:58,495
Min Jun.

39
00:02:59,065 --> 00:03:01,495
- Min Jun. - Director Park!

40
00:03:01,565 --> 00:03:03,905
- Are you okay, Min Jun? - Min Jun!

41
00:03:05,265 --> 00:03:06,405
Min Jun, it's okay.

42
00:03:06,835 --> 00:03:09,975
- I'm here now. Just breathe. - Ms. Choi, to the hospital.

43
00:03:10,045 --> 00:03:11,205
I'll help him up.

44
00:03:11,975 --> 00:03:15,175
- Sir. - Min Jun, are you all right?

45
00:03:20,855 --> 00:03:21,885
Kim Myung Hui.

46
00:03:24,025 --> 00:03:25,025
You...

47
00:03:25,325 --> 00:03:27,895
I heard you threatened Mr. Song for evidence.

48
00:03:28,155 --> 00:03:31,665
How dare you threaten my people behind my back?

49
00:03:32,965 --> 00:03:33,995
Your people?

50
00:03:34,965 --> 00:03:37,365
There's no such evidence, but even if there were,

51
00:03:37,935 --> 00:03:41,175
Geun Tae would never betray me.

52
00:03:41,675 --> 00:03:45,045
No matter what tricks you pull to get rid of me,

53
00:03:45,805 --> 00:03:48,045
neither Geun Tae nor Park Tae Ho...

54
00:03:48,415 --> 00:03:50,645
could ever abandon me.

55
00:03:51,715 --> 00:03:52,715
Is that so?

56
00:03:53,255 --> 00:03:55,015
I guess we'll have to wait and see.

57
00:03:59,995 --> 00:04:00,995
That...

58
00:04:02,055 --> 00:04:03,365
The nerve of her!

59
00:04:18,875 --> 00:04:21,415
I'm okay now. You should go home.

60
00:04:22,615 --> 00:04:26,015
No way. What if you suddenly get another headache?

61
00:04:26,145 --> 00:04:27,985
I've settled down, so I'm okay.

62
00:04:29,155 --> 00:04:31,925
He's right. It's late. You should get going.

63
00:04:34,655 --> 00:04:35,655
All right.

64
00:04:36,265 --> 00:04:38,425
Get some rest. See you tomorrow.

65
00:04:38,595 --> 00:04:39,595
Okay.

66
00:04:52,405 --> 00:04:53,415
What is it?

67
00:04:56,985 --> 00:04:59,415
- Mother. - If this is about Hyun Jun,

68
00:05:00,215 --> 00:05:01,215
just drop it.

69
00:05:01,485 --> 00:05:03,655
Hyun Jun didn't do anything wrong.

70
00:05:03,755 --> 00:05:05,185
I may have kept my distance...

71
00:05:05,255 --> 00:05:06,795
because his mother was intimidating...

72
00:05:06,795 --> 00:05:08,355
and I was jealous of how different we were,

73
00:05:08,855 --> 00:05:11,125
but he was always on my side.

74
00:05:11,595 --> 00:05:14,735
I'm sure he was, even at the time I can't remember.

75
00:05:15,535 --> 00:05:19,435
This time, I want to be there for him.

76
00:05:28,775 --> 00:05:32,145
I'll handle this matter myself,

77
00:05:32,485 --> 00:05:33,785
so stay out of it.

78
00:05:49,765 --> 00:05:52,105
Is Min Jun all right?

79
00:05:53,975 --> 00:05:55,305
He has a bit of a headache.

80
00:05:56,845 --> 00:05:57,845
I see.

81
00:06:14,355 --> 00:06:15,355
You okay?

82
00:06:17,125 --> 00:06:18,125
I'm good.

83
00:06:19,465 --> 00:06:22,035
- What brought this on again? - It's just...

84
00:06:22,795 --> 00:06:25,035
This happens whenever I feel like I'm about to remember something.

85
00:06:26,775 --> 00:06:27,775
I see.

86
00:06:29,075 --> 00:06:31,305
Don't rush it. Take your time.

87
00:06:45,125 --> 00:06:46,425
(Genotyping Report)

88
00:06:49,825 --> 00:06:53,835
What are you waiting for? Show this to Chairman Park.

89
00:06:54,835 --> 00:06:57,565
This is enough to make him divorce Oh Jung Ran in a heartbeat.

90
00:06:58,235 --> 00:07:01,575
And Min Jun will be the sole heir to the Adele Group.

91
00:07:02,675 --> 00:07:04,875
This can bring the war to an end.

92
00:07:05,545 --> 00:07:06,615
I suppose so.

93
00:07:07,275 --> 00:07:09,885
But Oh Jung Ran won't take this lying down.

94
00:07:10,545 --> 00:07:14,455
She'll be consumed by revenge and come after Min Jun again.

95
00:07:15,115 --> 00:07:18,385
We already went through this once when we exposed her past, remember?

96
00:07:19,225 --> 00:07:22,125
Then, how are you going to use this?

97
00:07:22,395 --> 00:07:25,265
I'm going to take Oh Jung Ran down in the most painful way possible...

98
00:07:25,825 --> 00:07:29,965
with no way for her to ever harm Min Jun again.

99
00:07:37,875 --> 00:07:41,075
How dare you play me for a fool?

100
00:07:41,145 --> 00:07:44,515
You promised the development rights and then you stabbed me in the back.

101
00:07:45,015 --> 00:07:49,885
How much did they pay you? Tell me how much more you want.

102
00:07:49,955 --> 00:07:51,085
Tell me!

103
00:07:51,085 --> 00:07:54,795
I did it to protect my reputation, not because of the money.

104
00:07:55,325 --> 00:07:56,325
What?

105
00:07:56,625 --> 00:07:57,725
Your reputation?

106
00:07:57,725 --> 00:08:00,595
They blackmailed me over my corruption.

107
00:08:01,295 --> 00:08:04,665
On top of that, they know all about my dealings with you.

108
00:08:04,765 --> 00:08:07,035
How could I hand over the development rights?

109
00:08:07,035 --> 00:08:08,305
If I had,

110
00:08:08,605 --> 00:08:10,605
they would've reported me immediately!

111
00:08:10,875 --> 00:08:15,115
Then we'd both have been in trouble, not just me.

112
00:08:15,175 --> 00:08:16,175
Why you...

113
00:08:20,755 --> 00:08:24,355
If you want the rights that badly, you should partner with them.

114
00:08:26,555 --> 00:08:28,625
- What? - CEO James Lee.

115
00:08:29,095 --> 00:08:32,495
JKL Partners is an investment firm isn't it?

116
00:08:32,925 --> 00:08:34,235
They can't handle...

117
00:08:34,235 --> 00:08:37,535
a five-billion-dollar project on their own.

118
00:08:38,405 --> 00:08:41,775
They must be looking for a partner to work with,

119
00:08:42,275 --> 00:08:43,505
so you should reach out to them.

120
00:08:54,385 --> 00:08:55,915
That Park Hyun Jun...

121
00:08:56,955 --> 00:08:58,325
made a huge decision.

122
00:08:59,755 --> 00:09:02,295
I think showing him Chairman Park threatening you...

123
00:09:02,695 --> 00:09:03,965
really got to him.

124
00:09:05,425 --> 00:09:07,465
So the only thing left is to convince Chairman Park?

125
00:09:09,065 --> 00:09:11,105
What do you think he'll do?

126
00:09:13,275 --> 00:09:17,305
He's too greedy to pass on a five-billion-dollar project.

127
00:09:18,045 --> 00:09:19,575
It might take some time,

128
00:09:20,275 --> 00:09:21,515
but he'll come around eventually.

129
00:09:25,985 --> 00:09:27,185
That means...

130
00:09:28,855 --> 00:09:30,555
this marriage will happen.

131
00:09:32,725 --> 00:09:34,225
I can't believe you're getting married like this.

132
00:09:35,325 --> 00:09:36,925
Are you still against it?

133
00:09:36,995 --> 00:09:38,525
I'm upset, that's all.

134
00:09:38,525 --> 00:09:40,035
If it weren't for Park Tae Ho and Choi Yu Na,

135
00:09:40,095 --> 00:09:41,865
your wedding could've been perfect.

136
00:09:43,435 --> 00:09:45,435
You would've had fun planning it too.

137
00:09:45,765 --> 00:09:49,035
I'll be doing my own kind of wedding prep...

138
00:09:50,045 --> 00:09:52,905
by changing the minds of those who stand in my way.

139
00:09:54,275 --> 00:09:56,315
But whether it'll be fun is debatable.

140
00:10:05,255 --> 00:10:06,625
Jung Ran.

141
00:10:06,925 --> 00:10:10,395
Don't react out of anger. Hear me out.

142
00:10:10,795 --> 00:10:14,365
I wasn't trying to betray you.

143
00:10:14,535 --> 00:10:16,705
I was afraid you'd do something reckless again.

144
00:10:16,705 --> 00:10:18,105
I've heard enough. Leave!

145
00:10:42,155 --> 00:10:45,065
If you're here to threaten me again, save your breath.

146
00:10:45,695 --> 00:10:49,365
You already know what happened based on Jung Ran's reaction.

147
00:10:50,465 --> 00:10:53,835
I told her everything,

148
00:10:54,305 --> 00:10:55,975
and I don't intend to betray her.

149
00:11:01,475 --> 00:11:03,845
What's this?

150
00:11:03,845 --> 00:11:05,245
See for yourself.

151
00:11:14,625 --> 00:11:16,795
Hyun Jun is your...

152
00:11:16,795 --> 00:11:18,195
My Hyun Jun!

153
00:11:19,995 --> 00:11:21,295
No, you can't.

154
00:11:22,135 --> 00:11:23,435
Leave him out of this!

155
00:11:23,435 --> 00:11:24,735
Exactly.

156
00:11:25,405 --> 00:11:28,505
What has your son done to deserve this?

157
00:11:29,075 --> 00:11:33,645
The one to blame is Oh Jung Ran, for hiding this massive secret.

158
00:11:34,575 --> 00:11:36,685
If I can get Oh Jung Ran divorced...

159
00:11:37,415 --> 00:11:39,945
and kicked out of the Adele family,

160
00:11:41,415 --> 00:11:45,025
I might consider leaving Hyun Jun out of it.

161
00:11:45,625 --> 00:11:46,625
What?

162
00:11:46,995 --> 00:11:48,295
Now that it's come to this,

163
00:11:49,625 --> 00:11:52,325
there's no avoiding the truth.

164
00:11:52,825 --> 00:11:56,965
But I'll let you choose which truth gets revealed.

165
00:11:57,605 --> 00:12:01,405
We can reveal that Oh Jung Ran tried to kill Min Jun,

166
00:12:03,905 --> 00:12:08,145
or we can reveal who Hyun Jun's real father is.

167
00:12:09,445 --> 00:12:11,115
Choose one.

168
00:12:11,685 --> 00:12:14,055
I can't give you much time.

169
00:12:15,285 --> 00:12:16,315
(Genotyping Report)

170
00:12:31,505 --> 00:12:33,235
Hyun Jun...

171
00:12:33,475 --> 00:12:36,105
Not my Hyun Jun.

172
00:12:43,175 --> 00:12:44,785
Unbelievable.

173
00:12:44,945 --> 00:12:48,085
Look at the time. Shouldn't Yu Na be home by now?

174
00:12:49,715 --> 00:12:51,655
Is she on a date this late?

175
00:12:52,625 --> 00:12:55,355
Do you think Min Jun and Yu Na...

176
00:12:55,855 --> 00:12:57,165
are getting serious?

177
00:12:58,295 --> 00:13:00,965
This is a ticking time bomb, I tell you.

178
00:13:01,795 --> 00:13:03,805
If Min Jun gets his memory back,

179
00:13:04,935 --> 00:13:06,605
it'll all be for nothing.

180
00:13:07,135 --> 00:13:10,945
But Yu Na says she's happy and she wants this.

181
00:13:11,975 --> 00:13:15,215
I feel like the least we can do is help her out.

182
00:13:19,045 --> 00:13:21,255
Hey. Yu Na, you.

183
00:13:22,115 --> 00:13:24,925
Get over here. Come here and sit down, you hear?

184
00:13:25,825 --> 00:13:26,825
Sit.

185
00:13:28,455 --> 00:13:32,295
Have you been with Park Min Jun this entire time?

186
00:13:33,225 --> 00:13:35,335
Yes, we went to the office together.

187
00:13:36,165 --> 00:13:38,505
Then Min Jun got a headache,

188
00:13:38,505 --> 00:13:40,805
so we went to the doctor and headed home.

189
00:13:40,975 --> 00:13:41,975
That's why I came home late.

190
00:13:42,705 --> 00:13:45,345
He really leans on me whenever he's in pain.

191
00:13:47,515 --> 00:13:50,645
Are you going to keep pretending to be Jin Ju...

192
00:13:51,315 --> 00:13:52,715
and deceiving Min Jun like this?

193
00:13:54,055 --> 00:13:56,785
Can you really not do without him?

194
00:13:56,785 --> 00:13:57,925
I can't, okay?

195
00:14:00,325 --> 00:14:02,095
If I can just win Min Jun's heart,

196
00:14:02,495 --> 00:14:04,025
I can become part of the Adele family.

197
00:14:04,225 --> 00:14:08,935
You silly girl. It's not his heart you need to worry about.

198
00:14:09,165 --> 00:14:10,865
You need to secure something real for yourself.

199
00:14:11,265 --> 00:14:13,035
What? Something real?

200
00:14:13,105 --> 00:14:16,505
What good is a man's fickle heart?

201
00:14:16,735 --> 00:14:19,145
In the end, all that matters is your status and title.

202
00:14:20,105 --> 00:14:21,875
- Her title? - That's right.

203
00:14:22,615 --> 00:14:25,885
If it's true that Park Min Jun really relies on you,

204
00:14:26,145 --> 00:14:28,855
then tell him to get you reinstated at the company right away.

205
00:14:29,285 --> 00:14:30,485
Reinstated?

206
00:14:38,165 --> 00:14:39,925
Why isn't he answering his phone?

207
00:14:40,535 --> 00:14:43,395
He has no right to ignore me after trying to sell me out.

208
00:14:43,465 --> 00:14:45,365
The person you have called is unavailable.

209
00:14:45,965 --> 00:14:46,975
Your people?

210
00:14:47,505 --> 00:14:50,645
Is that so? I guess we'll have to wait and see.

211
00:14:52,575 --> 00:14:56,275
She was too confident for someone who just got caught blackmailing.

212
00:14:58,045 --> 00:15:01,085
I need to find out what dirt she threatened him with.

213
00:15:02,715 --> 00:15:04,825
Why won't he answer the phone?

214
00:15:12,525 --> 00:15:14,795
I thought I made myself perfectly clear.

215
00:15:15,165 --> 00:15:17,705
I guess losing your memory doesn't change who you really are.

216
00:15:18,265 --> 00:15:19,265
How dare you show up here?

217
00:15:19,505 --> 00:15:21,505
I came because I have some news for you.

218
00:15:22,435 --> 00:15:24,575
The development rights the chairman was desperately trying to get?

219
00:15:25,175 --> 00:15:26,775
My father secured them.

220
00:15:28,015 --> 00:15:29,015
The development rights?

221
00:15:29,545 --> 00:15:31,545
The one he was discussing with Assemblyman Kwon?

222
00:15:31,885 --> 00:15:34,855
If I marry Hyun Jun, I'll convince my father...

223
00:15:35,415 --> 00:15:38,925
to partner with Adele Group on the exclusive development deal.

224
00:15:39,785 --> 00:15:43,565
Then Hyun Jun and I would lead the project for Adele Group.

225
00:15:44,425 --> 00:15:48,695
If the project succeeds, Hyun Jun will be named Adele Group's heir.

226
00:15:49,635 --> 00:15:53,675
What? Are you saying Hyun Jun will become the successor?

227
00:15:54,405 --> 00:15:57,905
Naturally, he can't go to the US if he's involved in this project.

228
00:15:58,545 --> 00:16:01,215
So you don't have to worry about him leaving.

229
00:16:04,045 --> 00:16:06,415
I think the chairman will come around soon, too.

230
00:16:07,255 --> 00:16:09,185
Please think it over.

231
00:16:13,995 --> 00:16:15,055
Mother.

232
00:16:18,665 --> 00:16:20,065
Wait. Hold on.

233
00:16:22,965 --> 00:16:25,035
I want a straight answer.

234
00:16:25,765 --> 00:16:29,435
Why do you want to marry Hyun Jun if you've lost all your memories?

235
00:16:30,645 --> 00:16:33,645
Because Hyun Jun loves me.

236
00:16:34,445 --> 00:16:36,675
Still, you'd marry a man you don't even remember?

237
00:16:37,615 --> 00:16:40,315
Not remembering him helped me see him for who he really is.

238
00:16:40,815 --> 00:16:42,885
He protected me when I lost my memory,

239
00:16:43,315 --> 00:16:44,655
reassured me with a smile,

240
00:16:45,125 --> 00:16:47,355
and promised to give me the world.

241
00:16:48,355 --> 00:16:51,495
I could feel his genuine love and concern...

242
00:16:52,095 --> 00:16:53,095
for me.

243
00:16:54,235 --> 00:16:55,635
With Hyun Jun by my side,

244
00:16:55,935 --> 00:16:58,835
I'll have all the support I need, even as part of the Adele family.

245
00:17:00,065 --> 00:17:03,205
Are you saying you have feelings for him?

246
00:17:04,445 --> 00:17:08,075
So please, give us your blessing to marry.

247
00:17:09,175 --> 00:17:10,175
Mother.

248
00:17:17,925 --> 00:17:19,685
So we'll get the rights, Hyun Jun will be named successor,

249
00:17:20,055 --> 00:17:21,855
and she's really in love with him?

250
00:17:27,665 --> 00:17:30,135
Director Seo, I need to see you for a minute.

251
00:17:30,565 --> 00:17:32,905
Get me everything you have on Chloe...

252
00:17:33,165 --> 00:17:36,175
and all the details on the exclusive development rights.

253
00:17:37,375 --> 00:17:39,575
What were you doing while Assemblyman Kwon was betraying us?

254
00:17:40,175 --> 00:17:43,645
No, while Chloe's father was scheming behind our backs,

255
00:17:44,315 --> 00:17:45,345
what exactly were you doing?

256
00:17:46,015 --> 00:17:48,915
You promised perfection. What is this mess?

257
00:17:50,585 --> 00:17:52,755
- I'm sorry. - Darn it!

258
00:17:53,185 --> 00:17:56,695
I knew I should've left this to Oh Jung Ran.

259
00:17:59,265 --> 00:18:01,935
What's done is done, sir.

260
00:18:03,065 --> 00:18:05,165
If you tell me what you want to do next,

261
00:18:05,565 --> 00:18:07,135
I'll find a way to make it happen.

262
00:18:16,145 --> 00:18:17,885
What is it this time?

263
00:18:18,045 --> 00:18:20,785
There's something we didn't settle during our last conversation.

264
00:18:22,015 --> 00:18:24,925
As for the terms for the Adele Group and my family to join forces,

265
00:18:25,425 --> 00:18:28,195
I only mentioned one of the two conditions.

266
00:18:29,095 --> 00:18:30,395
Join forces?

267
00:18:31,065 --> 00:18:32,695
You mean a joint development project?

268
00:18:34,095 --> 00:18:36,935
If the chairman agrees to my terms, that is.

269
00:18:38,805 --> 00:18:42,175
Didn't you ask for an apology?

270
00:18:43,205 --> 00:18:45,845
Yes. I should clear my name of the allegations...

271
00:18:45,845 --> 00:18:47,445
that I sold trade secrets.

272
00:18:49,115 --> 00:18:50,485
You've lost your memories,

273
00:18:51,115 --> 00:18:52,745
but you're sure you were framed?

274
00:18:53,485 --> 00:18:55,855
You had no evidence to back up your claim.

275
00:18:56,515 --> 00:18:59,325
You would've found evidence if any existed,

276
00:18:59,625 --> 00:19:01,895
and my father insists it never happened.

277
00:19:03,055 --> 00:19:05,265
So, what's your other condition?

278
00:19:06,565 --> 00:19:09,665
Please approve my marriage to Hyun Jun.

279
00:19:12,465 --> 00:19:15,375
You'll just give in to that boy's stubbornness?

280
00:19:15,705 --> 00:19:18,875
What you call stubbornness, I see as love.

281
00:19:20,275 --> 00:19:23,145
Hyun Jun and I have confirmed our feelings for each other.

282
00:19:32,725 --> 00:19:34,525
So if I apologise and give my approval,

283
00:19:34,895 --> 00:19:38,565
will Adele Group become a partner...

284
00:19:40,065 --> 00:19:41,435
in this development project?

285
00:19:42,835 --> 00:19:44,505
If Hyun Jun and I get married,

286
00:19:44,835 --> 00:19:47,505
we won't just be partners. We'll be family.

287
00:19:56,215 --> 00:19:59,115
She's winning Chairman Park over.

288
00:20:00,285 --> 00:20:03,115
If Chloe marries Hyun Jun with the development rights in hand,

289
00:20:03,855 --> 00:20:05,725
I'll be at a disadvantage in the fight for succession.

290
00:20:07,125 --> 00:20:08,195
But...

291
00:20:19,035 --> 00:20:20,735
(Park Hyun Jun)

292
00:20:22,135 --> 00:20:23,275
What brings you to the office?

293
00:20:24,775 --> 00:20:26,005
I just met with the chairman...

294
00:20:26,575 --> 00:20:29,315
and asked him to approve our marriage.

295
00:20:30,375 --> 00:20:33,915
So? Did my father get angry and give you a hard time again?

296
00:20:34,855 --> 00:20:38,525
No, he seemed more interested in the development rights.

297
00:20:40,025 --> 00:20:42,925
I think he'll approve our marriage soon.

298
00:20:44,165 --> 00:20:45,725
Right. I see.

299
00:20:48,635 --> 00:20:49,695
This is...

300
00:20:51,005 --> 00:20:52,165
what's best for you, right?

301
00:20:55,235 --> 00:20:57,275
I'll get going then.

302
00:21:08,085 --> 00:21:09,085
I'm sorry,

303
00:21:12,155 --> 00:21:13,155
and thank you.

304
00:21:14,195 --> 00:21:15,255
What?

305
00:21:16,255 --> 00:21:19,325
I just felt like I needed to thank you.

306
00:21:34,745 --> 00:21:35,745
Did you forget something?

307
00:21:44,255 --> 00:21:45,325
What brings you here?

308
00:21:46,555 --> 00:21:48,655
I was hoping we could have lunch together.

309
00:21:50,155 --> 00:21:51,165
You and me?

310
00:22:00,005 --> 00:22:01,005
Wait.

311
00:22:01,735 --> 00:22:03,235
You invited Mr. Song too?

312
00:22:05,045 --> 00:22:06,175
What an unlikely group.

313
00:22:07,745 --> 00:22:11,085
Hyun Jun, I heard you decided to marry Chloe.

314
00:22:11,945 --> 00:22:13,985
With the exclusive development rights at stake,

315
00:22:14,255 --> 00:22:15,655
I wanted to discuss it.

316
00:22:17,785 --> 00:22:18,785
What about Mr. Song?

317
00:22:19,685 --> 00:22:20,755
He's here on Ms. Oh's behalf.

318
00:22:21,995 --> 00:22:25,425
I thought you'd be more comfortable with Mr. Song than with her.

319
00:22:28,495 --> 00:22:29,495
Am I wrong?

320
00:22:30,265 --> 00:22:31,535
Well, I suppose so.

321
00:22:35,605 --> 00:22:38,775
Hear what Hyun Jun has to say and report back to Ms. Oh.

322
00:22:39,605 --> 00:22:40,605
What?

323
00:22:44,685 --> 00:22:45,685
Yes, of course.

324
00:22:57,195 --> 00:22:59,265
Anyway, Hyun Jun,

325
00:23:00,095 --> 00:23:01,865
what do you think of your father?

326
00:23:04,805 --> 00:23:08,075
I think of him as the chairman, not my father.

327
00:23:08,905 --> 00:23:09,905
Is that it?

328
00:23:11,575 --> 00:23:14,015
Aren't there any perks to being the chairman's son?

329
00:23:14,675 --> 00:23:15,675
Perks?

330
00:23:17,145 --> 00:23:20,015
I guess there is one good thing.

331
00:23:20,545 --> 00:23:22,515
Really? What's that?

332
00:23:22,955 --> 00:23:23,955
Thanks to him,

333
00:23:25,055 --> 00:23:28,555
I'm the heir to the Adele Group and have a stake in the company.

334
00:23:29,955 --> 00:23:33,565
Because now I can give Baek Jin Ju everything she needs.

335
00:23:36,935 --> 00:23:38,605
Are you fond of being the Adele Group's heir...

336
00:23:39,505 --> 00:23:42,175
and having the title that comes with it?

337
00:23:44,405 --> 00:23:47,875
What if you were to lose that title?

338
00:23:49,075 --> 00:23:50,145
Ms. Kim, please.

339
00:23:54,355 --> 00:23:58,155
You were ready to give it all up and leave for the US with Chloe.

340
00:23:58,655 --> 00:24:03,295
But now being Adele Group's heir has become important to you?

341
00:24:05,165 --> 00:24:07,935
Let's just say it's too useful to throw away now.

342
00:24:10,735 --> 00:24:14,075
Then if you lost your status as the Adele Group's heir,

343
00:24:14,935 --> 00:24:16,035
you'd be lost.

344
00:24:17,875 --> 00:24:18,875
Well,

345
00:24:20,445 --> 00:24:21,775
I suppose I'd be useless then.

346
00:24:37,355 --> 00:24:38,625
What on earth is this?

347
00:24:40,565 --> 00:24:43,135
I thought you and your son could have a nice meal together.

348
00:24:43,665 --> 00:24:44,665
Ms. Kim!

349
00:24:46,565 --> 00:24:50,135
I was just reminding you since you seemed hesitant.

350
00:24:51,345 --> 00:24:53,345
Please hurry, for your son's sake.

351
00:24:54,415 --> 00:24:57,785
I had no idea you were this cruel and terrifying.

352
00:24:59,815 --> 00:25:02,955
How can you of all people say that?

353
00:25:04,725 --> 00:25:06,955
You helped Oh Jung Ran kill my sister.

354
00:25:08,025 --> 00:25:10,965
You protect Oh Jung Ran while she targets my son.

355
00:25:12,365 --> 00:25:16,495
You were part of her crimes. That makes you an accomplice.

356
00:25:20,105 --> 00:25:23,875
And from the looks of it, Hyun Jun really values his title...

357
00:25:24,605 --> 00:25:26,105
as the heir to the Adele Group.

358
00:25:28,375 --> 00:25:31,545
So if you want to protect him, you'd better hurry.

359
00:25:53,805 --> 00:25:56,005
I can't believe Hyun Jun isn't Father's son.

360
00:25:56,735 --> 00:25:59,605
I wonder when and how Mother plans to reveal the truth.

361
00:26:00,475 --> 00:26:04,245
Father will definitely kick Hyun Jun out, too.

362
00:26:12,955 --> 00:26:16,095
If it's true that Park Min Jun really relies on you,

363
00:26:16,425 --> 00:26:18,925
then tell him to get you reinstated at the company right away.

364
00:26:23,835 --> 00:26:25,265
What are you thinking about so hard?

365
00:26:27,305 --> 00:26:28,305
It's nothing.

366
00:26:29,535 --> 00:26:30,575
What is it?

367
00:26:31,105 --> 00:26:33,345
Come on. There's nothing you can't tell me.

368
00:26:34,845 --> 00:26:36,345
Tell me what's wrong.

369
00:26:40,845 --> 00:26:44,155
It's nothing. I feel a little stifled, that's all.

370
00:26:46,555 --> 00:26:50,155
I'm sure you're feeling cooped up just staying at home.

371
00:26:51,825 --> 00:26:54,365
So when are you going back to work?

372
00:26:55,165 --> 00:26:57,195
- Back to work? - Yes.

373
00:26:57,905 --> 00:27:00,235
You were fine when we visited the office.

374
00:27:00,535 --> 00:27:04,405
With me by your side, you'll have no trouble settling in.

375
00:27:06,205 --> 00:27:08,715
Why don't we ask your mother...

376
00:27:09,075 --> 00:27:10,875
if we can both go back to work?

377
00:27:12,445 --> 00:27:13,445
How about it?

378
00:27:20,655 --> 00:27:21,725
I'll think about it.

379
00:27:29,465 --> 00:27:30,465
Park Min Jun.

380
00:27:31,435 --> 00:27:33,365
You smile at me and you even lean on me,

381
00:27:34,305 --> 00:27:36,605
so why does it feel like you're keeping me at arm's length?

382
00:27:39,545 --> 00:27:41,175
I need to get us back to work together...

383
00:27:42,275 --> 00:27:44,215
and make him depend on me more.

384
00:27:47,215 --> 00:27:50,185
You're saying Chloe's father's investment firm is solid?

385
00:27:51,185 --> 00:27:54,325
If we secure the development rights, the project will be successful?

386
00:27:55,595 --> 00:28:00,495
Yes. If we can, partnering with them would be our best bet.

387
00:28:00,725 --> 00:28:03,865
I'm sure the chairman would come to the same conclusion.

388
00:28:05,565 --> 00:28:08,105
So, should I let her marry my son?

389
00:28:09,435 --> 00:28:12,105
If you consider the succession battle,

390
00:28:13,245 --> 00:28:14,675
it's not a bad deal.

391
00:28:16,045 --> 00:28:17,945
She's hiding that huge secret of hers...

392
00:28:18,715 --> 00:28:20,245
and still focused on his marriage and succession?

393
00:28:21,455 --> 00:28:22,515
How could she?

394
00:28:26,285 --> 00:28:27,925
So you're saying she's beneficial to us.

395
00:28:29,655 --> 00:28:31,965
All right, you may go now.

396
00:28:32,325 --> 00:28:33,325
Yes, ma'am.

397
00:28:40,635 --> 00:28:44,205
There's that hateful, self-righteous look again.

398
00:28:45,075 --> 00:28:48,475
Like mother, like son. Both are filthy and insolent.

399
00:28:48,545 --> 00:28:50,275
Who are you calling filthy?

400
00:28:51,185 --> 00:28:54,245
If you ask me, you're the one who's filthy.

401
00:28:54,685 --> 00:28:57,785
What? Did you just call me filthy?

402
00:28:58,825 --> 00:29:01,595
- How dare you... - What do you think you're doing?

403
00:29:04,525 --> 00:29:06,795
Great, now you're ganging up on me.

404
00:29:08,965 --> 00:29:10,035
That's enough.

405
00:29:11,865 --> 00:29:14,505
You're both dead meat.

406
00:29:14,805 --> 00:29:15,805
Ms. Oh.

407
00:29:23,915 --> 00:29:25,585
Every last one of you...

408
00:29:52,145 --> 00:29:53,145
What?

409
00:29:55,145 --> 00:29:57,575
Where have you been all day?

410
00:29:58,085 --> 00:29:59,815
There's no one on my side here.

411
00:29:59,815 --> 00:30:01,915
At the very least, you should be with me.

412
00:30:02,215 --> 00:30:04,555
Do you have any idea how humiliated I was today?

413
00:30:07,285 --> 00:30:09,595
That brat Park Min Jun called me filthy.

414
00:30:09,895 --> 00:30:13,295
Did his memory loss make him crazy? How could he...

415
00:30:14,795 --> 00:30:16,665
I should've finished him back then.

416
00:30:17,465 --> 00:30:18,465
Just you wait.

417
00:30:18,835 --> 00:30:21,505
- I'll find a chance to do it again. - Again?

418
00:30:23,735 --> 00:30:25,805
You're going to try and harm Min Jun again?

419
00:30:26,945 --> 00:30:29,875
If he has to die, I'll do it. Why not?

420
00:30:31,315 --> 00:30:32,645
So you feel no remorse,

421
00:30:34,215 --> 00:30:37,015
and you don't intend to stop. Is that it?

422
00:30:38,185 --> 00:30:39,455
I do have regrets.

423
00:30:39,825 --> 00:30:42,395
I'm in this mess because I didn't finish him off back then.

424
00:30:44,695 --> 00:30:45,765
I knew it.

425
00:30:48,135 --> 00:30:49,435
You need to get away from this place.

426
00:30:50,265 --> 00:30:51,265
What do you mean by that?

427
00:31:08,315 --> 00:31:09,315
What is it?

428
00:31:11,325 --> 00:31:12,525
Sir, I have something to report.

429
00:31:14,255 --> 00:31:15,455
Which is?

430
00:31:15,855 --> 00:31:16,855
This concerns Park Min Jun.

431
00:31:18,165 --> 00:31:21,195
The hit-and-run driver who tried to kill your son...

432
00:31:24,235 --> 00:31:25,365
was...

433
00:31:29,875 --> 00:31:30,875
your wife,

434
00:31:33,105 --> 00:31:34,175
Oh Jung Ran.

435
00:31:36,415 --> 00:31:37,415
What?

436
00:32:31,235 --> 00:32:34,265
(Pearl in Red)

437
00:32:34,335 --> 00:32:38,275
Butler Ok! Get Oh Jung Ran in here right now!

438
00:32:38,705 --> 00:32:41,045
I'm a murderer's son.

439
00:32:41,045 --> 00:32:44,175
My very existence disgusts me.

440
00:32:44,245 --> 00:32:47,085
Kim Myung Hui, you. What on earth did you say to him?

441
00:32:47,145 --> 00:32:49,085
What secret are you holding over his head?

442
00:32:49,755 --> 00:32:53,125
Mr. Song, it seems you haven't told her yet...

443
00:32:53,385 --> 00:32:56,855
that I know exactly who Hyun Jun's father is.
